&lt;li&gt;Manage 1–2 teams (approx. 4–10 engineers total). You own the full talent lifecycle: hiring, retention, professional development, and performance management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work as a strategic partner to Product Management to balance new feature development with the technical debt and maintenance required to keep the platform stable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead design reviews, ensure code is scalable, and keep the team focused on simple, pragmatic solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use Agile practices to deliver value in small, frequent cycles, maintaining tight feedback loops with customers, product, and quality teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enforce high standards for TDD, CI/CD, and automation to maximize velocity and maintain confidence in our releases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate discussions to remove blockers and keep the team moving toward sprint goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we’re looking for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
