&lt;li&gt;An experienced engineer who values simplicity and pragmatism, implementing the right technical solution for the current problem without over-engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A leader who favors giving the team context over exerting control, ensuring everyone understands the &quot;why&quot; so they can own the &quot;how.&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A mentor who has built diverse teams, developed career plans, and knows how to provide the frequent, direct feedback needed to win as a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A natural builder who is passionate about engineering excellence, from code review culture to high test coverage and automation.&lt;/li&gt;
